The paper deals with image-based rendering and uses a deep fully Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) for prediction, which suggests that it falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also deals with light field reconstruction, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of a learning-based approach also suggests that it could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
